Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Riverside Square is a retail shopping center constructed in 1983 in North Lauderdale, Florida with Direct visibility to Rock Island Road. The roof was replaced in October 2014 with single membrane TPO & 20-year GAF manufacturer warranty, has a 10-year installer warranty & 10-year maintenance agreement. There are 54 total HVAC units on the roof with most of them having recently been replaced in 2014. Recent improvements in 2016 are the installation of 34 units LED Lights FLF Series of 100,000 hours with 10-year warranty for illumination of the parking lot and 59 LED 22W circular fixtures for the walkways & common areas. All surface-level parking spots were recently stripped in 2016. The gas connection is AmeriGas which services the entire building which is beneficial to restaurants. 
The B-2 community district is intended primarily to meet the shopping and limited-service needs of several neighborhoods or a substantial territory. Retail stores are intended to include convenience items, fashion, and durable good sales.

Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text:
Boca Raton continues to be one of South Florida’s hottest office markets and home to many corporate and regional headquarters. Just minutes from the LA Fitness Center, Boca Executive Airport, Florida’s Tri-Rail Station, and an abundance of shopping and dining opportunities, Yamato Office Center is the perfect location for your office. 

Boca Raton has historically had the lowest vacancy rate of Class A office space in cities of comparable size in Southeast Florida. This illustrates the growing desire by businesses, large and small, to call Boca Raton their home.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Yamato Office Center is conveniently situated just off I-95 in the heart of Boca Raton and is close to all of the South Florida major airports.  Yamato Office Center is highly sought after by companies who enjoy abundant amenities. 

The property is composed of two office buildings located at 999 and 1001 Yamato Road. Both buildings feature beautifully appointed lobbies and landscaping, outstanding Yamato Road exposure, secured card access, and more.
